{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"substring-before","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring-before","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath 참고 문서</a></b>: <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 요소</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 함수</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 축</a>\n</div><p></p>\n<p><br>\n <code>substring-before</code> 함수는 첫 번째 인수에서 두 번째 인수가 나타난 앞의 나머지를 반환합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ea.b5.ac.eb.ac.b8","title":"구문","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">substring-before(<i>haystack</i> ,<i>needle</i> )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.9d.b8.ec.88.98","title":"인수","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect2\">\n  <i>\n   <code>haystack</code></i>\n </dt>\n <dd>\n  평가할 문자열. 이 문자열의 부분이 반환됩니다.</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect3\">\n  <i>\n   <code>needle</code></i>\n </dt>\n <dd>\n  찾을 부분 문자열.\n  <i>\n   <code>haystack</code></i>\n  에서\n  <i>\n   <code>needle</code></i>\n  의 첫 출현 앞의 문자열이 반환됩니다.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.b0.98.ed.99.98","title":"반환","isH3":true,"content":"<p>문자열.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a3.bc.ec.9d.98","title":"주의","isH3":true,"content":"<p>XSL 예:</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">&lt;xsl:value-of select=\"substring-before('1999/04/01','/')\" /&gt;\n</pre>\n<p>출력</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">1999\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a0.95.ec.9d.98","title":"정의","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-substring-before\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.2</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_.ec.a7.80.ec.9b.90","title":"Gecko 지원","isH3":true,"content":"<p>지원함.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"substring-before 함수는 첫 번째 인수에서 두 번째 인수가 나타난 앞의 나머지를 반환합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"substring-before","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"substring-before","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"substring-before","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"substring-before","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/xpath/functions/substring-before","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/xpath/functions/substring-before/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring-before","title":"substring-before"}],"pageTitle":"substring-before - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}